Key Match Events: Maxey hit a game-winning three-pointer with 23.7 seconds left
Yabusele blocked a potential tying layup with 14 seconds left
Pre-Game Insights: Joel Embiid, Paul George, Kyle Lowry and Andre Drummond all sat out for Philadelphia
Washington played without leading scorer Jordan Poole and Malcolm Brogdon
Post-Match Reflections: Fans who did attend the game saw Maxey go off late
Maxey struggled at times as the go-to scorer this season with Embiid and George out so often
Miscellaneous Highlights: Tickets on the secondary market were going for less than $10 each in the lower 100 level right before tipoff
Kuzma appeared to get away with a travel on a bucket that gave Washington a 103-101 lead
Washington made only 6 of 9 free throws
